<!DOCTYPE concept PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Concept//EN" "concept.dtd">
<concept id="_4_3_1_the_canvas_model_has_following_advantages">
    <title>4.3.1 The canvas model has following advantages</title>
    <shortdesc>Advantages of the Canvas model</shortdesc>
    <conbody>
        <p>
            <ul id="ul_jgk_5my_pbc">
                <li>
                    <p>It gives a quick and concise overview of your project.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>It helps verify that what you're selling aligns with why, to whom, how, and
                        for how much.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>It lets you map out the key design elements and see how they interact with
                        each other.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>Allows you to understand the interaction between design elements and their
                        ordering.</p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </p>
    </conbody>
</concept>
